'''貝溫'''（'''Berwyn'''）是[[美國|美國]][[伊利諾州|伊利諾州]][[庫克縣_(伊利諾伊州)|庫克縣]]的一個城市。據2010年人口普查，貝溫總人口有56,657人<ref name="Census 2010">{{cite web| url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/DEC/10_DP/G001/1600000US1705573| title=Geographic Identifiers: 2010 Demographic Profile Data (G001): Berwyn city, Illinois| publisher=U.S. Census Bureau, American Factfinder| accessdate=February 7, 2013}}</ref>。貝溫在歷史上曾是一片沼澤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org/pages/1198.html|title=Stickney, IL|website=www.encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org|access-date=2016-02-27|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031042908/http://encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org/pages/1198.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，直到19世紀後期才開始發展，現在已經成為芝加哥重要的衛星城市<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/classified/realestate/ct-mre-0705-berwyn-bungalows-recognition-20150627-story.html|title=Berwyn bungalows one step closer to national historic recognition - Chicago Tribune|author=Chicago Tribune|date=27 June 2015|work=chicagotribune.com|access-date=2016-02-27|archive-date=2018-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825215801/http://www.chicagotribune.com/classified/realestate/ct-mre-0705-berwyn-bungalows-recognition-20150627-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

